<lb n="0919c03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0919006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說如意摩尼陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0919c04"/>
<lb n="0919c05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0919007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（西天…臣））二十字＝（（三藏法師））四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0919007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿傳法大師臣）二十字＝（三藏法師）四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0919007"><lem>西天<note n="0919008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔譯經〕－【明】</note><app n="0919008"><lem>譯經</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿
<lb n="0919c06"/>傳法大師<note n="0919009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0919009"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿傳法大師臣</rdg></app>施護奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0919c07"/><p>如是我聞。一時佛在舍衛國迦利哩城。爾時
<lb n="0919c08"/>世尊告尊者阿難。今有陀羅尼能除一切暴
<lb n="0919c09"/>惡雷電。汝當受持。此隨求如意寶經。過去如
<lb n="0919c10"/>來應正等覺親所宣說。我今亦說。於其世間
<lb n="0919c11"/>行大悲愍。利益安樂天上人間一切有情。阿
<lb n="0919c12"/>難白言唯然世尊。願樂欲聞我今受持。佛告
<lb n="0919c13"/>阿難汝等。當知東方有雷電名曰阿伽。南方
<lb n="0919c14"/>有雷電名曰設帝嚕。西方有雷電名曰哆&CB00425;
<lb n="0919c15"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>婆。北方有雷電名曰掃那摩&CB00135;。阿難若
<lb n="0919c16"/>有善男子善女人。知此雷電名號及住處方
<lb n="0919c17"/>位。一切雷電不怖彼人。若所在之處書寫此
<lb n="0919c18"/>雷電名號。受持供養。一切雷電而不能傷。爾
<lb n="0919c19"/>時世尊說此擁護真言章句</p>
<lb n="0919c20"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;彌&CB00135;彌&CB00135;彌孕<note place="inline">二合</note>馱哩<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0919c21"/>怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>路<note place="inline">引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>路吉&CB00135;輸羅播<note place="inline">引</note>尼&CB00135;囉乞
<lb n="0919c22"/>叉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">切身</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>尾&CB00135;用<note place="inline">二合</note>婆曳<note place="inline">引</note>毘
<lb n="0919c23"/>藥<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0919c24"/><p>爾時聖觀自在菩薩摩訶薩在大眾中。即從
<lb n="0919c25"/>座起合掌向佛。白佛言世尊。我於此正法。亦
<lb n="0919c26"/>說擁護真言章句</p>
<lb n="0919c27"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>尾曩<note place="inline">引</note>舍&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>怛也<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0919c28"/>體迦&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>怛也<note place="inline">二合</note>彌怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>輸弟目訖
<lb n="0919c29"/>帝<note place="inline">二合</note>尾摩&CB00619;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">引</note>娑迦<note place="inline">二合</note>哩<note place="inline">引</note>桉
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1403.0920a" n="0920a"/>
<lb n="0920a01"/>拏哩<note place="inline">引</note>半拏哩<note place="inline">引</note>濕尾<note place="inline">二合引</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>半拏囉&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>悉
<lb n="0920a02"/>&CB00135;麼<note place="inline">引</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>迦囉<note place="inline">引</note>羅迦閉羅賓&CB00344;羅<note place="inline">引</note>乞史
<lb n="0920a03"/><note place="inline">二合</note>那地目乞史<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞史<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞史<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0920a04"/>&CB00805;<note place="inline">切身引</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>羅沒哩<note place="inline">二合</note>底喻<note place="inline">二合</note>婆
<lb n="0920a05"/>曳<note place="inline">引</note>毘藥<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note>彌<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;舍滿<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;薩哩&CB00085;
<lb n="0920a06"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0920001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【明】</note><app n="0920001"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>沒哩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0920002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝引【明】</note><app n="0920002"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">引</rdg></app></note>阿哩也
<lb n="0920a07"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00085;路<note place="inline">引</note>吉帝<note place="inline">引</note>濕&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉帝<note place="inline">引</note>惹<note n="0920003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝婆【明】</note><app n="0920003"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>娑
<lb n="0920a08"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0920a09"/><p>爾時祕密主金剛手菩薩。往詣佛前合掌頂
<lb n="0920a10"/>禮。白佛言世尊。我今於此正法之中。亦說陀
<lb n="0920a11"/>羅尼真言章句</p>
<lb n="0920a12"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>母&CB00135;母&CB00135;母&CB00135;摩帝母&CB00135;摩
<lb n="0920a13"/>帝蘇摩帝摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>摩帝賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>摩帶
<lb n="0920a14"/><note place="inline">引</note>哩曩<note place="inline">二合引</note>悉底<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>半&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0920a15"/>播<note place="inline">引</note>尼囉憾涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>茶娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0920a16"/><p>世尊我此陀羅尼。名無能勝擁護有情。若人
<lb n="0920a17"/>書寫憶念。所有一切恐怖及其中夭悉令解
<lb n="0920a18"/>脫</p>
<lb n="0920a19"/><p>爾時大梵天王索訶世界主。白佛言世尊。我
<lb n="0920a20"/>為利益一切眾生。於此正法亦說陀羅尼真
<lb n="0920a21"/>言章句</p>
<lb n="0920a22"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>呬&CB00619;彌&CB00619;唧&CB00619;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0920a23"/>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩<note place="inline">二合</note>布哩<note place="inline">引</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩
<lb n="0920a24"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>尼<note place="inline">引</note>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00344;哩鼻<note place="inline">二合引</note>補瑟波
<lb n="0920a25"/><note place="inline">二合</note>設娑哆<note place="inline">二合</note>哩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0920004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）【明】</note><app n="0920004"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0920a26"/><p>世尊我此陀羅尼名梵天杖。擁護一切有情。
<lb n="0920a27"/>遠離中夭不生恐怖亦能除滅一切罪業。爾
<lb n="0920a28"/>時帝釋天主。詣佛前立合掌頂禮。白佛言世
<lb n="0920a29"/>尊。我今於此正法。亦說陀羅尼真言章<note n="0920005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">句＋（曰）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0920005"><lem>句</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">句曰</rdg></app></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1403.0920b" n="0920b"/>
<lb n="0920b01"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>沒馱麼<note place="inline">引</note>旦膩<note place="inline">引</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;&CB00135;憍
<lb n="0920b02"/><note place="inline">引</note>哩巘<note place="inline">引</note>馱<note place="inline">引</note>哩贊拏&CB00619;摩<note place="inline">引</note>鄧詣布訖&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0920b03"/>悉娑<note place="inline">引</note>羅沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>呬曩末馱用<note place="inline">二合</note>哆羅
<lb n="0920b04"/>尼滿&CB00418;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00619;&CB00135;計<note place="inline">引</note>作迦<note n="0920006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【三】</note><note n="0920006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉＝羅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0920006"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>枳舍&CB00085;
<lb n="0920b05"/>哩舍<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;哩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0920b06"/><p>世尊我此陀羅尼名金剛座。解脫一切怖畏。
<lb n="0920b07"/>遠離一切中夭</p>
<lb n="0920b08"/><p>爾時持國天王增長天王廣目天王多聞天王
<lb n="0920b09"/>俱詣佛前合掌頂禮。白佛言世尊。我等於此
<lb n="0920b10"/>正法。亦說陀<note n="0920007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羅〕－【明】</note><app n="0920007"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>尼真言章句</p>
<lb n="0920b11"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他補瑟閉<note place="inline">二合引</note>蘇補瑟閉<note place="inline">二合引</note>度波
<lb n="0920b12"/>波哩賀<note place="inline">引</note>哩<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>設悉帝
<lb n="0920b13"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>扇<note place="inline">引</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;哩目<note place="inline">二合</note>訖帝<note place="inline">二合引</note>夢&CB00344;&CB00619;曳<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0920b14"/>合</note>呬囉拏也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00344;哩鼻<note place="inline">二合引</note>娑&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>娑
<lb n="0920b15"/>哆<note place="inline">二合</note>尾帝<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0920b16"/><p>世尊我等四大天王作說陀羅尼名為無怖。
<lb n="0920b17"/>於其恐怖能施無畏。遠離中夭增延壽命</p>
<lb n="0920b18"/><p>爾時復有大海龍王。所謂大意龍王雷光龍
<lb n="0920b19"/>王。無熱惱龍王電舌龍王百光龍王。俱詣佛
<lb n="0920b20"/>所合掌頂禮白佛言世尊。我有陀羅尼名如
<lb n="0920b21"/>意寶。擁護有情。若人書寫讀誦。能除一切雷
<lb n="0920b22"/>電怖畏。一切中夭一切諸毒一切惡病。及不
<lb n="0920b23"/>吉祥鬼神亦不得便。世尊若持此真言。我等
<lb n="0920b24"/>龍類悉皆悲愍不生嫉&CB00107;。於意云何龍趣之
<lb n="0920b25"/>類行嫉&CB00107;心。若聞此法而無嫉&CB00107;。陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0920b26"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>阿惹哩<note place="inline">引</note>摩摩哩<note place="inline">引</note>阿蜜哩<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0920b27"/>合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>阿訖叉<note place="inline">二合</note>曳<note place="inline">引</note>阿尾也<note place="inline">二合</note>曳<note place="inline">引</note>奔尼
<lb n="0920b28"/>也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>曳<note place="inline">引</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>波&CB00425;
<lb n="0920b29"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>舍摩&CB00135;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>阿哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>奔拏
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1403.0920c" n="0920c"/>
<lb n="0920c01"/>燥<note place="inline">引</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>枳曳<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note n="0920008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝引夾註【元】【明】</note><note n="0920008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印＝<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">（引）</lem><rdg wit="【大】">引</rdg></app>夾註【元】【明】</note><app n="0920008"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>捺囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>舍&CB00135;
<lb n="0920c02"/>曳<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0920009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彌＝&CB00135;【元】【明】</note><app n="0920009"><lem>彌</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00135;</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>伽<note place="inline">引</note>舍&CB00135;曳<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0920c03"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0920c04"/><p>爾時世尊聞彼大梵天王天帝釋護世四天王
<lb n="0920c05"/>及大龍王等說此陀羅尼。讚言善哉善哉。能
<lb n="0920c06"/>令多人得大安藥。汝等護持流行正法。佛說
<lb n="0920c07"/>此經已。一切大眾天龍阿修羅乾達婆等。皆
<lb n="0920c08"/>大歡喜信受奉行</p>
<lb n="0920c09"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說如意摩尼陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
